{"tid":967710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【到處是紅線，到處是禁忌】港台金針獎　黃耀明致詞片段","createTime":"2019-01-03T17:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T03:30:01.000Z","uid":147314,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fb8921dd0330ee5a838942128f3c15d70cf4da7c","tid":967710,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:10:08.000Z","msg":"第四十一屆十大中文金曲「用心・聽」音樂會 金針獎得主：達明一派<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pCM1hKUJ5h0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpCM1hKUJ5h0&d=NGDs88IILeUySPzm2k3Y1xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d9caf151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pCM1hKUJ5h0</a><br />\n<br />\n前3後3分鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【十大中文金曲最高榮譽金針獎】致詞內容被港台過濾 黃耀明：希望大家守住廣東話<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190103/59102523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190103%2F59102523&d=NGDs88IILeUySPzm2k3Y1xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4b84c26e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190103%2F59102523&h=d0153369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190103/59102523</a>"},{"pid":"ea357e373b9315307efdf3eca2efac02f57eddd9","tid":967710,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:14:24.000Z","msg":"sorry 係頭3尾3分鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3320fb9561516714649b196628381602a05f77","tid":967710,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:17:45.000Z","msg":"劉以達支結打無線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：唔識, 呢d 應該已經有wifi/藍牙 做connect <br />\n其實唔明點解仲有人笑檸檬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98573c6ab3e807bda6cec3fc1e75a9618b9e3149","tid":967710,"uid":147314,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:27:30.000Z","msg":"敢言嘅明哥更爆料話佢嘅致詞內容被過濾：「我哋係土生土長嘅香港人，我哋一直以熟悉嘅廣東話唱出香港人故事，希望大家守住廣東話同埋我哋嘅文化，我哋經歷過香港嘅盛世同衰落，喺聖誕聽到有人播黃霑唱嘅聖誕歌提及鄧小平，令我諗起達明都唱過幾位領導人，來自百無禁忌嘅8、90年代，本來我要講幾句嘢，但畀人刪咗，今日我哋呢個城市到處都係禁忌，到處都係紅線，呢啲嘅紅線同埋禁忌，將會扼殺流行音樂同藝術嘅發展，我諗係每一個人嘅恐懼，亦都係我深深嘅恐懼，攞咗好多獎牌嘅呢度咁多位，上咗岸嘅我哋，受惠於香港盛世嘅我哋每一位，希望大家諗吓，有冇諗過我哋留低乜嘢畀下一代？重要嘅嘢講多次，願某地方，不需將愛傷害，抹殺內心的色彩，願某日子，不需苦痛忍耐，將禁色盡染在夢魂外。多謝大家。」"},{"pid":"bb2b85d89fb4fb3344269bf846ca11739830a8d2","tid":967710,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T17:31:31.000Z","msg":"一個我地喜愛既年代見證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab8c410adebe12bee8e5defb316e15d7a1ed398","tid":967710,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T22:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eee3790f162306c171bf10327fbfd94fba6c1f7","tid":967710,"uid":77196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:01:32.000Z","msg":"禁忌同紅線好大程度係果班得益者自我審查做成，肥彭當年真係冇講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d49be1aaea64a7e2beabbc4ee35e249742ee3b","tid":967710,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:12:01.000Z","msg":"香港人係抵俾中共收皮，自我滅亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d09e22e75df9a1de88b326e246923a1f9a658ef","tid":967710,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:13:12.000Z","msg":"皇后大道東<br />\n半斤八兩<br />\n太陽花<br />\n<br />\n。。。。<br />\n<br />\n呢類歌唔會再係香港主流歌曲中誕生<br />\n<br />\n只剩低情愛低俗音樂"},{"pid":"397eb841bad1235afa319ad57f253e27338b6be2","tid":967710,"uid":35430,"like":0,"disli